Interface IDefaultValueElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IDefaultValueElement
extends IEntity
    IDefaultValueElement: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    The default value consists of a number of elements. Each element is one byte long and the number of elements is specified by SduLength.
